latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Recieved this amazing skin care hamper from @mothersparsh 
All products of this brand are plant-based. 
So no silicon,parabens, dyes, SLS/SLES or harsh chemicals are present in their products.
More over it is an Indian brand and products are not high priced but their quality is superb, so no need to invest in costly foreign brands to get plant based products. 

In frame : 

1. Plant Powered Ultra-Rich Face Wash
Key Ingredients : Earth Marine Water, Vanilla Oil, Tejpatra Oil, Coconut Oil
Benefits : Deeply cleanses skin, without drying it out and has anti bacterial properties to prevent breakouts. 

2. Plant Powered Oatmeal & Honey Face Mask
Key Ingredients: Oatmeal Extracts, Honey, Avocado Oil, Kaolin
Benefits : Honey nourishes skin well and oatmeal helps to exfoliate skin and absorb impurities. It provides a smooth and glowing skin 

3. Plant Powered Under Eye Recovery Gel
Key Ingredients: Avocado Oil, Cucumber Extract, Almond Oil, Glycerin
Benefits : Helps to brighten eye area, fight drak circles and fine lines. 

4. Plant Powered Body Butter
Key Ingredients: Shea Butter, Cocoa Butter, Calendula Oil, Jojoba Oil
Benefits : Moisturies skin well and locks in moisture for a smooth, hydrated nad glowing skin. 

5. Plant Powered Ultra-Rich Face Cream
Key Ingredients: Kokum Butter, Lavender Oil, Shea Butter
Benefits : It helps to hydrate skin and locks moisture. Prevents aging and breakouts of skin.
